#Text=Katara says : " I guess that 's me . "
#Text=Sokka says : " Mm , not bad , not bad !
#Text=So , what do you think they 're talking about back there ?
#Text=" Sokka says : " Boring stuff I 'm sure .
#Text=Love , who she 's going to marry , how many babies she 's going to have .
#Text=" Aang says : " Yeah , dumb stuff like that ... Well , I 've got to find a bathroom .
#Text=" Wu says : " Your palms are so smooth .
#Text=Do you use moisturizer ?
#Text=" Katara says : " Actually , I have this special seaweed lotion .
#Text=I can get you some if you want .
#Text=So , do you see anything interesting in my love line ?
#Text=" Wu says : " I feel a great romance for you .
#Text=The man you are going to marry .
#Text=" Katara says : " Tell me more !
#Text=" Wu says : " I can see that he 's a very powerful bender .
#Text=" Sokka says : " Looks like someone had a pretty good bathroom break .
#Text=" Aang says : " Yeah ... when I was in there ... " Sokka says : " I do n't even want to know !
#Text=" Wu says : " Who 's next ?
#Text=" Sokka says : " Okay , let 's get this over with .
#Text=" Wu says : " Your future is full of struggle and anguish .
#Text=Most of it , self - inflicted .
#Text=" Sokka says : " But you did n't read my palms or anything !
#Text=" Wu says : " I do n't need to .
#Text=It 's written all over your face .
#Text=You there , come with me .
#Text=" Wu says : " This is the most reliable method of telling your fortune .
#Text=The bones never lie .
#Text=Go on , pick one .
#Text=Now throw it on the fire .
#Text=The heat makes cracks in the bone and I read the bone cracks to tell your destiny .
#Text="
